metadata.name: Enigma #1
metadata.description:
Enigma: a person or thing that is mysterious, puzzling, or difficult to understand.‚Äù 

Enigmatica is a blend of colors and textures, showing how we can explore both, together to create an emotional experience. Enigmatica features colors from the natural world; shades of red and pink from plants and flesh that can draw visions of blood and violence, warmth and birth, cool blue sadness, oceanic waves. Color ways and textures bring movement that examines human frustration through brush strokes, meditation through repetition. Each painting is an Enigma defined by the consciousness of each viewer.
